PROCLAMATION NO. 1261

RESERVING AND GRANTING OWNERSHIP IN FAVOR OF THE NATIONAL POWER CORPORATION CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN GENERAL AGUINALDO, MUNICIPALITY OF RAMON, PROVINCE OF ISABELA, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL ARROYO, President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby reserve and grant ownership in favor of the National Power Corporation (NPC) that certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in Barangay General Aguinaldo, Municipality of Ramon, Province of Isabela, Island of Luzon, subject to private rights if any there be, which parcel of land is more particularly described as follows:

